name: Dig To Escape
summary:
Dig to Escape

Grab your shovel and get digging!  

Outsmart sneaky moles, brawl with inmates, and take on wacky quests as you tunnel your way to freedom in the wildest prison break ever!

Dig for upgrades

Collect minerals and sell them to upgrade your tools. Better gear means bigger digs and more ways to escape.
